                <h2>Architected for people, not surveys.</h2>
                <p>The success of your people is a complex combination of empowerment, purpose, growth, and more. It’s a formula that continually evolves throughout the employee experience.</p>
                <p>Unlike survey providers, Glint is built on a people-centric architecture that captures data throughout the employee lifecycle, giving you a more complete picture of your people. And it’s designed to support complex, global organizations, regardless of how they’re organized — or how often they’re reorganized.</p>
